  <h1>ABOUT</h1>
</div>

<div class="about-page container">
  <div class="about-body">
    <p>Redcontroldeck is an imprint operated by Matt Kudlacz in Chicago.</p>
    <p>The name is a misheard lyric. The system is a way of marking outputs — writing, music, events, objects — with a common origin.</p>
    <p>It is not a company. It does not explain itself too much.</p>
